<title>
Cylinder Head Bolt Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "S8T40A1436025">Valve and Cylinder Head Disassembly and Reassembly:J24B</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
If they are reused, check thread diameter of cylinder head bolt (1) for deformation as follows and replace it with new one if thread diameter difference exceeds its limit.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<ptxt>
Measure each thread diameter of cylinder head bolt &#8220;A&#8221; at &#8220;a&#8221; and &#8220;B&#8221; at &#8220;b&#8221; using micrometer (3).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Then calculate difference in diameters (A &#8211; B). 
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If it exceeds limit, replace cylinder head bolt with new bolt.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Cylinder head bolt diameter measurement points
</title>
<ptxt>
&#8220;a&#8221;: 95.0 mm (3.74 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
&#8220;b&#8221;: 130.0 mm (5.12 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>
Cylinder head bolt diameter difference (deformation)
</title>
<ptxt>
Limit (A &#8211; B): 0.25 mm (0.0098 in.)
</ptxt>
